291
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,320
Let go!

292
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:37,720
Don't misinterpret things!

293
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,849
Even if you paid me,

294
00:19:43,857 --> 00:19:45,537
I wouldn't sleep with you!

295
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:46,660
Where are you going?

296
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,160
I'm going home.

297
00:19:48,320 --> 00:19:49,700
I don't want to be here.

298
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:51,404
Is your only good feature

299
00:19:51,428 --> 00:19:52,678
