300
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,620
What do you want?

301
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,000
Go to sleep.

302
00:20:02,060 --> 00:20:03,540
I'm not in the mood anymore.

303
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:05,500
Who would believe that?

304
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:08,000
Then go outside and catch a cold.

305
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:10,480
I'm going to sleep.

