334
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:16,940
And then you suddenly went home.

335
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,600
It's obviously weird.

336
00:23:26,060 --> 00:23:27,140
Yes.

337
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:29,660
Yes.

338
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:32,020
Oh, the repairs.

339
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:34,760
Yes.

340
00:23:35,840 --> 00:23:38,400
Yes, I'll pick it up tomorrow.

341
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,520
Yes.

342
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:42,460
Thank you.

343
00:23:46,500 --> 00:23:47,800
Great,

344
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:51,520
